;As you browse, Lightbeam reveals the full depth of the Web today, including parts that are not transparent to the average user.
Nabigatu ahala, Lightbeam-ek gaur egungo webaren sakonera osoa erakusten dizu, erabiltzaile arruntarentzat gardenak ez diren zatiak barne.


